@startuml StaticLoadBalancing

[*] --> SystemIdle

SystemIdle --> PowerAvailable : Power detected
PowerAvailable --> StationsInitialized : All stations online
StationsInitialized --> PowerAllocated : Divide power equally (25 kW each)

PowerAllocated --> Charging : Car connects to station
Charging --> Charging : Continue charging
Charging --> CarDisconnects : Car leaves or is fully charged
CarDisconnects --> PowerAllocated : Reallocate power (still equal)

PowerAllocated --> NoCarConnected : No car at station
NoCarConnected --> PowerAllocated : Still allocate power equally

@enduml